********************************************************************************
*                                                                              *
*      Input file for the Lagrangian particle dispersion model FLEXPART        *
*                       Please specify your output grid                        *
*                                   template                                   *
********************************************************************************

1.  ------.----       4X,F11.4
    $outlonlower       GEOGRAFICAL LONGITUDE OF LOWER LEFT CORNER OF OUTPUT GRID
    OUTLATLOWERONLEFT        (left boundary of the first grid cell - not its centre)

2.  ------.----       4X,F11.4
    $outlatleft       GEOGRAFICAL LATITUDE OF LOWER LEFT CORNER OF OUTPUT GRID
    OUTLATLOWERONLEFTTWERONLEFTTLOWER       (lower boundary of the first grid cell - not its centre)

3.  -----             4X,I5
    $numxgrid           NUMBER OF GRID POINTS IN X DIRECTION (= No. of cells + 1)
    NUMXGRID

4.  -----             4X,I5
     $numygrid           NUMBER OF GRID POINTS IN Y DIRECTION (= No. of cells + 1)
    NUMYGRID

5.  ------.-----      4X,F12.5
     $dxoutlon      GRID DISTANCE IN X DIRECTION
    DXOUTLON

6.  ------.-----      4X,F12.5
     $dyoutlat      GRID DISTANCE IN Y DIRECTION
    DYOUTLAT
